name: Wood_Leg_White_Accent_Chairs_In_White_(Set_of_2)_-_(As_Is_Item)
description: Add some extra seating with this pair of accent chairs from Baxton Studio. The retro-style chairs combine an ergonomic shape and a curved seat to offer you a comfortable seating experience. The construction and design include molded plastic finished with a durable matte, and the wooden legs are reinforced with black steel hardware to ensure stability. These contemporary accent chairs are ideal for your dining table or to add seating in your bedroom or family room. The wood legs contrast the matte finish of the chairs and have black plastic tips to protect your flooring.
